==English==

===Etymology===
"Hell" spelled out, referring to the fact that capital "L" looks like a [[hockey stick]].

===Noun===

'''HE-double-hockey-sticks'''

# {{cattag|[[euphemistically]]}} [[hell|Hell]].

===Usage notes===
May be spelled with varying levels of hyphen usage.

